Package: artcodex
Title: An R Client for Local Codex App-Server Sessions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Bobby", "Fatemi", email = "bfatemi@users.noreply.github.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Controls local 'Codex' app-server sessions from R over the
    standard input and output transport. It can start and resume threads,
    stream events, handle server requests, interrupt turns, request structured
    output, and retain serializable execution records for unattended
    workflows.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/bfatemi/artcodex
BugReports: https://github.com/bfatemi/artcodex/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-US
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    processx
Suggests:
    covr,
    lintr,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
SystemRequirements: Codex CLI with app-server support
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
